==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[characters]] per [[inch]]'''

# The number of typographic characters that fit on each inch of a line of printed type. The measurement applies mainly to [[font]]s that have the same width for each character ([[monospaced]]). Fonts with characters of varying widths can have an average cpi.
# The amount of characters per inch ("linear packing density") when storing data on certain types of [[magnetic]] media or tape, used to measure storage density that recoding medium possesses.

